metadata.name: Alizzz & Meowww in Technicolorland
metadata.description:
Follow the white cat!

It had Rainbow Orb realm! I just love an explosion of colors, be it vibrant, pastel or dark <3

I'm very thankful to the WoW team for everything they've done for me and this piece has been done lovingly and with Yam often in my mind through the process, remembering when she reached out nearly a year ago.

Strange Cintia's single edition for the WoW World S7's ArtDrop.
